Thabit (from Arabic ثابت; fixed) is a fixed width OpenType font family that
is supports Arabic script. It is developed by Arabeyes.org as part of Khotot
project.

The font is distributed under Open Font License, see the included OFL.txt for
more details.

Currently supported languages:
* Arabic (basic Arabic, no Quranic support yet)
* Pashto
* Farsi

You can visit our web page
http://www.arabeyes.org/project.php?proj=Khotot

